body:
To test this after running `docker-compose up --build`, you can run

```
$ docker run -it --rm --network grid_default  postgres psql -h db -U grid
Password for user grid: < type "grid_example" >
psql (11.2 (Debian 11.2-1.pgdg90+1))
Type "help" for help.

grid=# select * from block;
                                                             block_id                                                             | block_num |                         state_root_hash
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+-----------+------------------------------------------------------------------
 8bbf805bc297ee264c9aaae43f79c6730c4909be9766db0c9e74ef7b53eee24e58a46e41c14174385c0d1383a1ce35b271a0a230c965904a29fe35bb89db7679 |         0 | f5f0adfe399e64c6f22ccf678409e8a9b2e05ef704eacb74217ee19dcce08bfa
(1 row)
grid=#
```
Please add a note in the commit messages which describe the documents these are derived from, for reference purposes.
Sorted both contents of maintainers and codeowners files alphabetically.
